Package: spatcart
Title: Spatial classification trees
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Servane",
           family = "Gey",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "servane.gey@u-paris.fr",
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: spatcart provides classification trees adapted to bivariate marked point processes by using a splitting criterion associated with the Kcross interaction between marks proposed by Ripley. The package also provides the corresponding graphics.
